{"tid":2185335,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"資深副導演朱日紅離世，為香港電影界貢獻半世紀","createTime":"2020-09-02T07:48:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T07:49:22.000Z","uid":35221,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"515d4a74fb3dd923ef42702de58d7edca3420215","tid":2185335,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T07:48:14.000Z","msg":"【一路好走】資深副導朱日紅離世 為電影界貢獻半世紀<br />\n20200902<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/L45bnPbSjLf9Wqn0t4jCH8Iba1w=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AZ5Y63FE75AIZB5Q4BS6X4DF2M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FL45bnPbSjLf9Wqn0t4jCH8Iba1w%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAZ5Y63FE75AIZB5Q4BS6X4DF2M.jpg&h=ea1b35af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n資深香港電影副導演朱日紅（八姐）昨日離逝，享年86歲。章國明導演今日在Facebook悼念故友，他寫道：「正中嗰位係：朱日紅，我哋都叫佢做『八姐』，香港電影重點人物，我哋曾經一齊登上喜馬拉雅山，而家佢就獨自登上仙界，八姐再見！」<br />\n<br />\n電影工作者總會會長田啟文（田雞）接受《蘋果》訪問表示：「昨日中午有行家攞粥畀佢食仍好好，晚上佢喺梳化時，工人叫佢入房瞓先知佢走咗！佢嘅喪事，我哋會同佢家人商量，睇下需唔需要幫手！」<br />\n而曾經跟八姐合作無間的黃百鳴接受《蘋果》訪問，憶述跟對方共事：「八姐喺新藝城幫我哋做《開心鬼》系列副導演，佢係一個好資深副導演，又好心機照顧當時好頑皮嘅開心少女組班友，係好難得好好嘅電影人，我對佢相當尊敬。其實佢喺電影圈好長歷史，佢自細抱住馮寶寶拍戲，喺粵語片電影圈好有經驗，新藝城一開始時，所有好多電影都係八姐幫我哋做副導，佢真係副導演王，新藝城所有人都好尊敬佢。」<br />\n<br />\n人稱八姐的朱日紅擔任副導演接近60年，曾與李香琴、任冰兒、梁素琴、黎坤蓮、金影憐、許卿卿、英麗梨及譚倩紅等二幫花旦結義金蘭姊妹，合稱「九大姐」。1991年榮獲香港電影金像獎頒發專業精神獎，亦是第一位在台上獲獎的香港電影副導演，當年更是由周潤發頒獎予八姐。去年「香港電影副導演會」為表揚八姐多年來為電影界的專業貢獻，以及表揚她在副導演界的肯定地位，執委麥啟光與劉小慧在農曆新年間拜訪八姐，並邀請八姐為副導演會及一眾副導演們錄製了一段勉勵說話，藉此短片互相鼓勵，為香港電影界共同努力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/WVe_XyEutvr3aV_0iRuIw7oJZy0=/1083x895/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VLR3QF7CKZCBDDELMBWQ5VTJ6U.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWVe_XyEutvr3aV_0iRuIw7oJZy0%3D%2F1083x895%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVLR3QF7CKZCBDDELMBWQ5VTJ6U.JPG&h=8043cb44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第9屆香港電影金像獎專業精神獎，發哥拖著八姐上台領獎。(網上截圖)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200902/NXZVHKMUKFCVVEDTH43CGCXZXY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200902%2FNXZVHKMUKFCVVEDTH43CGCXZXY%2F&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXODrFCZ%2FFQqiuLijmhCLlc8%3D&h=933d110a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200902%2FNXZVHKMUKFCVVEDTH43CGCXZXY%2F&h=6cd116e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200902/NXZVHKMUKFCVVEDTH43CGCXZXY/</a>"},{"pid":"9727ac6abb7496b72c770e5c4889c6822ef382c0","tid":2185335,"uid":346260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T07:49:22.000Z","msg":"唔該借個位嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有用 post ,樓主可唔可以置頂？唔該曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係想保護自己同身邊嘅人？即刻入嚟睇吓!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[實用文] 教您點先可以保障私隱、網絡安全<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2185179\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2185179</a>"}]}